author: Corridor Crew
description:
Apple went to great lengths to film their F1 movie starring Brad Pitt. Including a big collaboration with F1 to get access to shoot on race days for an entire season, partnering with Sony to design and build 25 brand-new 4K full-sensor mini-cameras, and working with top-of-the-line VFX teams at Framestore and ILM.

Did the VFX take you out of the movie at any point?
title: The Lengths Apple went for F1 the Movie
